game.name: Crazy Dog Racing Fever
game.description:
The coolest adventure is in your town! Will you try to get participated in it and play with your favourite pet dog? So there is no need to waste your time anymore. Join Crazy Dog Racing Fever and be prepared to help your chosen wild go to run on the tracks and win some rewards in the popular animal crazy racing championship of 2020! It is not going to be easy at all as multiple types of dogs have got participated in the competition.  

It is now up to you how wisely you control your dog to get noticed in the world biggest dog race tournament! Choose your race out of multiple options including Tournament, Quick Race, Tiger US Dog, Cart, Wolf Vs Dog, and Cheeta Vs Dog and select your dog and get ready to enter the extremely crazy greyhound racing! Remember you will get the German Shephard dog initially, however you need money to upgrade your pet. Winsome races to earn money and coins in this free online HTML5 running game!

Common boys! It is time to participate in several fun competitions with multiple types of animals in this realistic 3D dog racing game! Make sure to guide him and make a way to the finish line first. You would have different race modes with extremely tricky championships and tournaments. Hurry up! Multiple pets like wolves, horses, tigers, and other animals are waiting for you. Use your cash to play with new dogs and customize your stadiums! Enjoy with all popular dog breeds to play online for free!
